dct_title_s: Map of the northern part of the State of Magdalena, U. S. of Colombia by Mr. F. A. A. Simons, 1879
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes elevation profile: Horizontal section between San Sebastian and Atanquez [vertical scale ca. 1:120,000]. Mr. Simons's routes shown in red. "The limits of the National Territory of Nevada, occupied by the Arhuacos Indians, is shewn by a dotted line." From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 1 (1879), no. 11, pp. 689-694; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
